node.text:
Witness a revolutionary way to experience luxury real estate. Utilizing the innovative first-person view drone technology, see how @luxury_listings is disrupting real estate marketing.

Listed by @clarencedebelle for $16,880,000, 6435 Madrona Crescent in #WestVancouver, is a sensational Southern-California-inspired contemporary masterpiece built by @alexbarbachkoff.

🎥🎬 Filmed and directed by @luxury_listings | Contact us to redefine your marketing today

#luxuryhomes #luxurylistings #mansion #westvancouver #horseshoebay #millionaire #dreamhome #modern #realestate #luxury #vancouver #bc #canada #homedecor
